title: [MINDSET] 4: "How To Build Your Confidence and Stop Losing Yourself" w/ Kylie McBeath
description: This week’s episode of the “You Turn Podcast w/ Ashley Stahl” will motivate you to look inward and “come back home” to your most authentic self. Kylie and Ashley discuss how to navigate the different stages of romantic relationships while still honoring one’s true self. Kylie prompts Ash to go deep with some thought-provoking questions about core values and relationships—tune in and answer the questions for yourself, too. As always, stick around for Ashley’s post-episode thoughts!
